title: Airbus - worldwide aircraft deliveries 2002 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of aircraft deliveries. In total the number of data points it has is 18.
Overall Number of aircraft deliveries has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
The highest Number of aircraft deliveries, of value 863.0 was reached at Year 2019
Minimum Number of aircraft deliveries about 303.0 was reached at Year 2002
